data.description: Opportunity awaits. Put your own stamp on this spacious well loved split level home centrally located close to everything Eastchester has to offer. Large living room with wood burning fireplace flows into the formal dining room. Eat-in kitchen. Spacious main bedroom includes a walk-in closet and en-suite bathroom. Walk up attic offers the possibility of a fourth bedroom, playroom, or home office. Flat private backyard features a large covered patio and rows of evergreens. Wide driveway offers plenty of parking. Walk to train, school, parks and shops. Lake Isle pool, tennis and golf membership available.
